title: ZULU Indestructible Beats! Compiled by Rock Savage South Africa
description:
ZULU Indestructible Beats!

A Collection of 90 Zulu and South African Tracks compiled by Rock Savage.

There is Dance Music, Jazz, Traditional and Indestructible Beats.

Included are Mango Groove, Ladysmith Black Mambazo, West Nkosi, Ipi N Tombi, Harry Belafonte, Miriam Makeba and Many More

This is a Original Collection and Rare.

Original Art Work Included.

All 90 Tracks are MP3s 192 or 256 kbps 44.100 kHz and Tagged

If you dont Dance to this then nothing will move you. 

Enjoy!
